# Markdown Governance

- Prefer concise Chinese unless the target file is already English.
- Keep documentation actionable, not essay-like.
- When adding a new workflow artifact, update the relevant repo entrypoint.
- Keep `commands/`, `skills/`, and operating docs aligned.
